OL,3,CWarning over 'worryingly hot'
OL,4,Cclassrooms as climate change worsens
OL,5,Cheatwaves
OL,7,F"This has been a mild summer by recent
OL,8,Fstandards, so it is scary to picture
OL,9,Fhow bad this will get when
OL,10,Ftemperatures well above 30C return."
OL,12,FHe warned that schools, like many of
OL,13,Fthe UK's buildings, were not set up
OL,14,Fand funded to deal with the higher
OL,15,Ftemperatures being seen because of
OL,16,Fclimate change.
