OL,3,CWarning over 'worryingly hot'
OL,4,Cclassrooms as climate change worsens
OL,5,Cheatwaves
OL,7,F"The weather used to just be small
OL,8,Ftalk but we now need our political
OL,9,Fleaders to ensure the country is
OL,10,Fbetter prepared for more extreme
OL,11,Fweather and to tackle the fossil fuel
OL,12,Fpollution that is causing it in the
OL,13,Ffirst place," he said.
OL,15,FIt comes after analysis from the Met
OL,16,FOffice shows the UK is seeing, on
OL,17,Faverage, more frequent periods of hot
OL,18,Fweather and an increase in extreme
OL,19,Frainfall, bringing challenges for
OL,20,Finfrastructure, health and wellbeing.
