OL,7,FBut the Government's plan to adapt to
OL,8,Fthe risks posed by climate change is
OL,9,Fcurrently being challenged in the High
OL,10,FCourt, by campaigners who claim the
OL,11,FTory administration's July 2023
OL,12,FNational Adaptation Programme (NAP)
OL,13,Ffails to properly respond to 61
OL,14,Fclimate change risks.
